## 第三方组件与引用

本项目依赖以下开源组件，遵循各自的许可证：

### PostgreSQL Core Database
- **URL**: https://www.postgresql.org/
- **License**: PostgreSQL License (MIT-style)
- **Version**: 18.x

### pgvector - Vector Similarity Search for PostgreSQL
- **GitHub**: https://github.com/pgvector/pgvector
- **License**: Apache License 2.0
- **Usage**: Vector type, HNSW index support, similarity functions

### Apache AGE (Apache Graph Extension)
- **URL**: https://age.apache.org/
- **License**: Apache License 2.0
- **Version**: 1.7.0
- **Usage**: Property Graph support, Cypher query language

### BGE-M3 Embedding Model (FlagEmbedding)
- **GitHub**: https://github.com/FlagOpen/FlagEmbedding
- **License**: Apache License 2.0
- **Model**: BAAI/bge-m3
- **Usage**: Text embedding generation (1024 dimensions)

### HNSW Algorithm Research Paper
- **Title**: Efficient and Robust Approximate Nearest Neighbor Search Using Hierarchical Navigable Small World Graphs
- **Authors**: Yuivii A. Malkov, Dmitry A. Yashunin
- **URL**: https://arxiv.org/abs/1603.09320
- **License**: Research Paper (for algorithm reference)

